  <h1 class="gd-h1">The Heliski Lodge Experience</h1>
  <p class="gd-byline" style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:12.5px;letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(--blue-soft);opacity:.9;margin:16px 0 0">By <a href="/about" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px">Vegard Knudsen</a> · Founder, Heliski Travel · Updated 8 Jun 2026</p>
  <p class="gd-lede">A heliski week is not only about the runs. It is about the hours off the mountain too: the warmth you come home to, the hot tubs by the water, the shared meals and the easy company of your group. This is a field note on life at the lodge, the other half of what makes an Iceland trip so complete, before you explore <a href="/packages">the packages</a> and <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
</div></section>
